Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.25,1:27:46.78,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}真实与谎言的虚势
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.87,1:27:52.24,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}藏不住失落的心声
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.33,1:27:54.54,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Star Ring Child
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.65,1:28:03.54,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}握住颤动的心 奏响生命
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.63,1:28:11.72,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}稚嫩小手绘下的一切
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.86,1:28:19.53,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仿如未来跃然纸上
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.68,1:28:46.61,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不愿挥手的少年 依依不舍
